description.main: Decoherence is a non-fungible artwork token by Christopher J. Sanborn (ArtCASA). To view this token and others, visit https://artcasa.gallery.

nft_object.attestation: I, Christopher J. Sanborn, originator of the work herein, hereby commit this artwork to the BitShares blockchain, to live as the token named ARTCASA.DCOHRNCE, as an original, first-edition, tokenized digital artwork.
nft_object.narrative:
Coherence,
Each piece,
Individual,
In phase.

Forgetful,
Then disordered,
Becomes Decoherence.
nft_object.title: Decoherence
